data.description:
Welcome to this MUST SEE!
Stunning and meticulously maintained two-story home that has undergone extensive updates and renovations. Including a tastefully manicured landscaping all around.

The property boasts a desirable layout with the MASTER BEDROOM and SECOND BEDROOM PLUS A OFFICE/FLEX ROOM located on the LOWER LEVEL.

The home exudes a sense of elegance and style, with attention to detail evident in every corner. You will be greeted by a spacious and inviting living area featuring stunning cathedral ceilings. Ascending to the upper level, you will discover a versatile loft area. parking even enough for an RV or other toys. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers easy access to local amenities, schools, shopping centers, and recreational facilities.This home's exceptional maintenance and updates extend throughout the property.
